title: Android 12L Beta 3 now available, adds support for Pixel 6 series
content:
Samsung dominated the technology world this Wednesday, with its announcements of the Galaxy S22 and Galaxy Tab S8 devices, but Google apparently wants some time in the spotlight too. The third beta release of Android 12L is now available, and for the first time, it’s available to try out on the Pixel 6 and Pixel

The post Android 12L Beta 3 now available, adds support for Pixel 6 series appeared first on xda-developers.
description: Google has released Beta 3 of Android 12L, which adds support for the Pixel 6 series and fixes a bunch of bugs.
